Kyrgyz foreign trade insurance company set up . Russia ' s second biggest insurance company SAO Ingosstrakh said on Thursday it had become one of the founders of a new Kyrgyz insurance company Kyrgyzinstrakh . The other founders include Central - Asia trust company Orient , and Kyrgyz state insurance companies Kamkor - S and Akzhol , Ingosstrakh said in a statement . It said the chief goals of the new company was to set up an insurance market for Kyrgyzstan foreign trade , to insure foreign investment in mining and power sectors of the industry , and to cover building and ecology risks . - - Julie Tolkacheva , Moscow Newsroom , + 7095 941 8520 
